{"tid":1182547,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰往北京航班起飛前疑冒煙　乘客行程延誤","createTime":"2019-06-02T09:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T09:21:25.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"430f6d380b9f8a4ee87c62e30135d5c0530143ba","tid":1182547,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T09:20:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因管理不善而從全球最佳航空公司排名榜排名節節下跌的國泰航空</span></ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，一班原定於今晨(2日)9時起飛前往北京的CX390航班，於8時08分乘客尚未登機時，在赤鱲角機場停機坪進行起飛前例行檢查，期間機底疑突然冒煙，消防處接報派出多輛消防車到場戒備，經檢查後發現並無起火。 <br />\n<br />\n國泰航空發言人表示，有關航班在進行例行檢查期間，冷氣系統懷疑因電路問題出現故障，故遂按照既定程序通知消防人員戒備。國泰一向以乘客及機組人員的安全為首要考慮，因此立即安排另一航機接載乘客，並於早上9時47分啟程出發，國泰航空就事件對乘客帶來之不便深表歉意。機管局發言人表示，機場運作無受影響。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190602/mobile/bkn-20190602154446332-0602_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190602%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190602154446332-0602_00822_001.html&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI1u%2BYei5PLor89YqF%2FSdhCs%3D&h=a76eb07c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190602/mobile/bkn-20190602154446332-0602_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2990112501babe4729ea028cca359f81837b602b","tid":1182547,"uid":1241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T09:21:25.000Z","msg":"睇topic都知係咩報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}